RestGateway --> CallService : routes to
RestGateway --> GroupService : routes to
RestGateway --> StatusService : routes to
RestGateway --> FileService : routes to
RestGateway --> PostService : routes to
RestGateway --> FeedService : routes to
RestGateway --> ExploreService : routes to
RestGateway --> FollowService : routes to
RestGateway --> CommentService : routes to

